Install java
************
1. download jdk 1.7 (java) from http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/javase/downloads/jdk7-downloads-1880260.html
2. Click "Accept license agreement"
3. Click  jdk-7u45-windows-i586.exe to download

Install idea
************
1. Download IntelliJIdea 12 from http://www.jetbrains.com/idea/download/
2. Click "Download" on Community edition free version